RawLine: SDM_1101042105,那金丹雖能激發武學潛能，副作用卻不可小覷，據大小姐所說，\n她體內時時戾氣沸騰，若不訴諸武力發洩，便心癢難耐，不能自己。,那金丹虽能激发武学潜能，副作用却不可小觑，据大小姐所说，\n她体内时时戾气沸腾，若不诉诸武力发泄，便心痒难耐，不能自己。

Items.mt: That golden elixir can stimulate martial arts potential, but the side effects are not to be underestimated, according to Missy, <<\n>> her body is always seething with hostility, and if she does not resort to force to release it, she will have an itch that is unbearable, and she cannot control herself.
